com.orchestranetworks.service
Class Archive

java.lang.Object
  com.orchestranetworks.service.Archive
public abstract class Archive
extends Object

An instance of this class references an EBX5 archive.

An archive represents a set of contents from a repository. It is used to propagate content from one repository to another.

The implementations of this class are light-weight references to their underlying resources. For example, they do not open a file stream if a file is provided.

An EBX5 archive must be generated by an archive export procedure.

See Also:
ProcedureContext.doExportArchive(Archive), ProcedureContext.doImportArchive(Archive)
